Download the free app and place an order in a few clicks!
We will quickly find a free car near you.
Watch the approaching car on your phone screen in real time! While the car is coming to you, you will see the arrival time, as well as photos and personal rating of the driver.
Order to the airport / transfer to the airport:
"YES Taxi" is a great opportunity to make an order and get to the airport in comfort.

Key features of the application:
- Ordering a car without calling the dispatcher. Mark a point on the map; no need to write a long address manually;
-  Preliminary calculation of the trip cost;
- Search for a car based on the fare and your wishes (child seat, receipt, etc.);
- The app shows detailed information about the driver and their car;
- The driver's movement is visible on the map;
- After the trip, leave a review about the quality of service;
- Save popular addresses and quickly select them;
- A sound signal will inform you about the arrival of the car;
- Purchase history. Repeat order. Return trip.
